WEBVTT

01:39.370 --> 01:43.470
[Road to Success]

01:44.710 --> 01:47.950
[Episode 31]

01:48.070 --> 01:49.900
[Wang Fa]

02:01.040 --> 02:03.070
Chengye, you should sign it too.

02:04.710 --> 02:05.920
D-Drunk.

02:07.040 --> 02:10.240
Arrogant.

02:24.970 --> 02:26.640
In the beginning,

02:29.000 --> 02:32.150
I was just a slacker
who hadn't walked out of pain.

02:35.400 --> 02:38.120
After the first meeting with you,

02:40.560 --> 02:43.400
I was actually really happy.

02:46.990 --> 02:49.990
Because you all really sucked.

02:51.360 --> 02:53.040
I thought...

02:53.220 --> 02:54.770
I thought that

02:54.910 --> 02:57.260
after playing one round with you,

02:59.040 --> 03:01.550
I could retire with success

03:02.190 --> 03:04.360
and continue to be a slacker.

03:04.730 --> 03:05.470
Ms. Lin,

03:05.470 --> 03:07.730
you are really not sparing our feelings.

03:08.090 --> 03:09.260
-Yeah.
-Exactly.

03:21.660 --> 03:24.150
But I never thought

03:28.120 --> 03:30.400
that I could actually

03:31.840 --> 03:34.190
make it to the finals with you guys.

03:42.650 --> 03:44.530
Everyone, stand up again.

03:48.960 --> 03:50.100
I want...

03:50.710 --> 03:53.960
Once again, I want to grandly

03:53.960 --> 03:55.579
thank

03:56.000 --> 03:58.060
Mr. Win,

03:58.560 --> 04:00.710
Coach Wang Fa.

04:03.000 --> 04:06.080
He provided our football team

04:06.080 --> 04:09.400
with the most professional
football training ground

04:09.400 --> 04:10.910
and hotel accommodation in Hongjing.

04:10.910 --> 04:12.190
He

04:12.840 --> 04:14.890
used the power of money

04:14.910 --> 04:19.269
to support us in sprinting for
the championship.

04:22.440 --> 04:24.600
Just clapping is useless.

04:24.680 --> 04:27.640
Let's prove it
to him with practical actions.

04:27.680 --> 04:29.270
First bow.

04:29.270 --> 04:32.190
-First bow.
-Thank you, Coach.

04:32.190 --> 04:33.720
Second bow.

04:33.720 --> 04:35.920
-Thank you, Coach.
-Thank you, Coach.

04:35.920 --> 04:38.800
-Third bow.
-All right. That's enough.

04:38.800 --> 04:40.240
Don't interrupt me.

04:40.560 --> 04:41.560
Fourth bow.

04:41.560 --> 04:43.190
-Thank you, Coach.
-Thank you, Coach.

04:43.190 --> 04:45.270
-Fifth bow.
-Go home.

04:45.270 --> 04:46.480
Listen to me.

04:46.480 --> 04:47.310
You still have a match to play.

04:47.310 --> 04:48.630
-Alright.
-Alright.

04:48.630 --> 04:49.890
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

04:49.920 --> 04:51.270
-Let's go.
-We're off, Coach.

04:51.270 --> 04:52.750
Fifth bow.

04:54.070 --> 04:56.120
-Stop.
-Sixth bow.

04:56.120 --> 04:57.240
All right.

04:57.240 --> 04:59.070
-Don't hurt yourself.
-Seventh bow.

04:59.070 --> 04:59.870
Let's go home.

05:03.830 --> 05:05.000
Fifteenth bow.

05:05.000 --> 05:05.950
With our level...

05:05.950 --> 05:07.270
Twentieth bow.

05:07.950 --> 05:09.680
Thirtieth bow.

05:10.270 --> 05:11.430
Fortieth bow.

05:13.070 --> 05:17.630
Fiftieth bow. Sixtieth bow.

05:19.270 --> 05:20.070
A bit hungry.

05:20.070 --> 05:21.160
What to eat?

05:55.040 --> 05:58.600
[Fu Xinshu]

06:08.030 --> 06:09.990
[Wen Cheng]

06:18.690 --> 06:20.080
[Wen Chengye]

06:25.870 --> 06:26.600
Use this one.

06:34.010 --> 06:34.890
Why...

06:34.909 --> 06:36.320
why are you here?

06:37.390 --> 06:38.940
Ms. Lin is drunk.

06:38.970 --> 06:40.230
No one locked the door.

06:40.830 --> 06:41.800
You actually could have

06:41.800 --> 06:44.200
just pushed the front door open
and come in.

06:48.750 --> 06:49.640
I...

06:50.750 --> 06:52.150
I forgot to take my stuff.

06:53.330 --> 06:54.300
Really?

07:02.070 --> 07:03.270
Do you want to sign it?

07:17.460 --> 07:20.220
[Wen Chengye] [Fu Xinshu]

07:30.660 --> 07:33.150
[Wen Cheng]

07:37.700 --> 07:41.580
[Wen Chengye] [Fu Xinshu]

07:44.060 --> 07:45.420
I'm very happy

07:46.190 --> 07:48.520
that we can play football together again.

07:59.030 --> 08:01.140
W-Whatever you say.

08:11.390 --> 08:14.680
Fu Xinshu. Wen Chengye.

08:24.600 --> 08:27.540
We're home. Wait.

08:27.980 --> 08:30.620
Thank you for taking me home.

08:30.680 --> 08:31.480
Alright.

08:31.500 --> 08:33.630
You've bowed over 100 times on the way.

08:33.840 --> 08:34.669
Come on, take your shoes off.

08:34.669 --> 08:36.030
That many?

08:36.600 --> 08:37.480
Yes.

08:38.360 --> 08:39.480
You counted?

08:40.960 --> 08:42.120
I did.

08:44.390 --> 08:46.910
I should go wash up.

08:49.000 --> 08:50.260
Can you do it yourself?

08:50.680 --> 08:52.130
Yes.

08:52.150 --> 08:53.890
Don't worry about me.

08:56.290 --> 08:57.890
Take it easy.

09:50.870 --> 09:52.710
Done washing.

09:57.550 --> 10:00.030
Time to sleep. Turn off the lights.

10:07.890 --> 10:09.220
Are you uncomfortable?

10:12.670 --> 10:13.360
Here.

10:13.720 --> 10:14.870
Drink some water.

10:22.330 --> 10:23.280
Get a good rest.

10:23.600 --> 10:25.860
Contact me anytime if you need anything.

10:30.060 --> 10:31.020
Wang Fa.

10:34.390 --> 10:36.720
I took a shower,

10:39.870 --> 10:42.070
but why do you smell even better than me?

10:53.790 --> 10:55.810
♪ I caught your eyes ♪

10:56.340 --> 10:58.790
♪ On the summer night ♪

10:59.190 --> 11:04.660
♪ Like stars that glow so bright ♪

11:06.210 --> 11:08.620
♪ A spark in my heart ♪

11:09.170 --> 11:15.090
♪ Lost in a dream secretly ♪

11:18.580 --> 11:23.820
♪ With the evening breeze
whispering in my ear ♪

11:24.430 --> 11:30.110
♪ Fireworks bloom across the sky ♪

11:30.710 --> 11:33.010
♪ Shimmering in your eyes ♪

11:33.670 --> 11:39.490
♪ And spreading into
a gentle sea of stars ♪

11:39.600 --> 11:40.670
Lin Wanxing.

11:41.360 --> 11:42.960
You are really drunk.

11:42.730 --> 11:44.560
♪ Every night ♪

11:45.470 --> 11:47.160
♪ I reach for starlight ♪

11:47.710 --> 11:49.700
♪ Wandering through dreams with you ♪

11:49.320 --> 11:52.440
We are the champions.

11:50.490 --> 11:52.780
♪ I follow the beat of my heart ♪

11:53.440 --> 11:56.100
♪ Like dust floating in the air ♪

11:57.040 --> 11:58.870
♪ Because of your love ♪

11:57.790 --> 12:01.150
We are the champions.

11:59.730 --> 12:04.230
♪ I shine brilliantly ♪

