13:02.450 --> 13:04.880
♪ Shimmering in your eyes ♪

13:05.410 --> 13:11.680
♪ And spreading into
a gentle sea of stars ♪

13:45.510 --> 13:46.510
I'm going for a morning run.

13:46.510 --> 13:48.870
Drink some orange juice
to sober up when you wake up.

13:48.870 --> 13:52.120
Someone said "We are the champions"
18 times in her sleep.

13:52.300 --> 13:54.480
I've received your wish to win.

13:54.480 --> 13:55.630
Working on it.

13:57.750 --> 13:59.910
We all know who wasn't paying attention

13:59.910 --> 14:01.510
at that time.

14:02.840 --> 14:05.080
But I never thought

14:06.910 --> 14:09.240
