14:10.630 --> 14:12.750
make it to the finals with you guys.

14:19.350 --> 14:24.320
I want to grandly thank

14:24.790 --> 14:26.930
Mr. Win once again.

14:27.360 --> 14:28.870
First bow.

14:28.870 --> 14:31.380
-First bow.
-Thank you, Coach.

14:31.720 --> 14:33.440
Second bow.

14:33.440 --> 14:35.670
-Thank you, Coach.
-Thank you, Coach.

15:08.370 --> 15:14.300
♪ Waiting for a dark cloud
to pass by you ♪

15:11.010 --> 15:13.640
Besides your grandparents
in this world,

15:14.870 --> 15:19.680
♪ Listen closely to its cries ♪

15:15.120 --> 15:17.120
