16:35.620 --> 16:36.470
Yes.

16:45.660 --> 16:46.390
Thank you.

16:46.410 --> 16:47.940
You're welcome. Take care.

16:49.860 --> 16:51.590
♪ The rainbow deep within your heart ♪

16:52.290 --> 16:54.670
