♪ My heart remains true,
bound in the name of love ♪

17:59.200 --> 18:01.410
♪ I cross the wild wasteland
till you come into view ♪

18:02.230 --> 18:04.940
♪ Bringing me fiery courage ♪

18:05.590 --> 18:08.140
♪ And standing with me
