18:09.060 --> 18:11.560
♪ Till you burst into my world ♪

18:12.680 --> 18:15.100
♪ Side by side,
we chase our shared dreams ♪

18:15.950 --> 18:18.280
♪ I gaze into your resolute eyes ♪

18:19.500 --> 18:22.130
♪ Marching forward to
our shared tomorrow ♪

18:23.250 --> 18:24.540
♪ I'm waiting for you ♪

18:38.030 --> 18:39.330
You sing really well.

18:39.360 --> 18:41.890
Why don't you join
our band as the lead singer?

18:42.630 --> 18:43.760
I'll think about it.

18:46.440 --> 18:49.460
Okay. Our next song is "Sunrise."

18:49.800 --> 18:51.920
-Great!
-Great!

18:55.580 --> 18:57.510
[Scholarly Progress]

18:57.250 --> 18:58.010
Coach.

18:57.510 --> 19:03.040
[Final Tactical Analysis]

18:58.310 --> 18:59.160
Are we going to discuss

18:59.160 --> 19:01.420
the tactics against Yongchuan Hengjiu?

19:03.130 --> 19:06.390
[Yongchuan Hengjiu's 4-1-4-1 Formation]

19:04.200 --> 19:06.480
Hengjiu's 4-1-4-1 formation.

19:06.720 --> 19:07.720
It consists of 4 defenders,

19:07.720 --> 19:08.440
one defensive midfielder,

19:08.440 --> 19:09.350
4 midfielders,

19:09.350 --> 19:10.280
and one forward.

19:10.690 --> 19:12.230
You're amazing.

19:12.440 --> 19:14.300
We just need to do our best anyway.

19:14.440 --> 19:16.040
Being the runner-up is fine.

19:16.200 --> 19:17.160
Right, Boss?

19:19.740 --> 19:21.030
You are quick-witted.

19:21.060 --> 19:23.460
What are the weaknesses of this formation?

19:24.160 --> 19:25.110
Their defensive midfielder

19:25.110 --> 19:26.880
is the key to their passing routes.

19:25.320 --> 19:26.640
[Yongchuan Hengjiu's 4-1-4-1 Formation]

19:26.920 --> 19:29.160
But the forward is definitely Qin Qiechu.

19:29.160 --> 19:31.290
Who will be the defensive midfielder?

19:32.770 --> 19:34.970
It should be their captain, Fang Sulun.

19:35.640 --> 19:37.320
I've checked Hengjiu's info.

19:37.340 --> 19:38.680
In this league,

19:38.680 --> 19:39.350
our focus

19:39.350 --> 19:41.480
has always been on their forward,
Qin Qiechu.

19:41.480 --> 19:42.640
But actually, their captain's

19:42.640 --> 19:44.070
strength shouldn't be underestimated
either.

19:44.070 --> 19:45.870
He personally scored 11 goals

19:45.900 --> 19:47.900
and provided 18 effective assists.

19:48.680 --> 19:49.270
Right.

19:49.430 --> 19:51.350
Although he is not as fast as Qin Qiechu,

19:51.350 --> 19:52.620
his ball control is solid

19:52.620 --> 19:53.750
and consistent.

19:53.880 --> 19:54.750
Good analysis.

19:55.310 --> 19:56.660
You all look the part.

19:56.750 --> 19:58.440
Coach, how do we break it?

19:59.880 --> 20:00.000
[Yongchuan Hengjiu's 4-1-4-1 Formation]

20:00.080 --> 20:01.540
[Aggressive end-to-end football]

20:00.590 --> 20:03.650
-Aggressive end-to-end football.
-Aggressive end-to-end football.

20:03.650 --> 20:05.790
How can we hold our own against
Yongchuan Hengjiu in this attacking clash?

20:05.790 --> 20:07.860
It's like bringing a knife to a gunfight.

20:07.860 --> 20:08.040
[Aggressive end-to-end football]

20:08.040 --> 20:11.980
[Distance covered by players]

20:08.920 --> 20:09.350
Look.

20:10.000 --> 20:13.660
Here is the comparison
of the total distance covered by everyone.

20:16.000 --> 20:16.790
Fu Xinshu.

20:17.150 --> 20:20.070
[Wen Chengye] [Lin Lu] [Fu Xinshu]

20:17.550 --> 20:19.070
From 5,100 meters

20:19.200 --> 20:21.070
to 6,830 meters now.

20:21.830 --> 20:24.490
You can now completely
control the whole field.

20:25.990 --> 20:26.960
[Distance covered by players]

20:26.110 --> 20:26.680
Qin Ao.

20:27.240 --> 20:28.760
From 5,530 meters

20:28.790 --> 20:30.480
to 7,300 meters now.

20:28.900 --> 20:30.960
[Qin Ao] [Chen Jianghe]

20:30.480 --> 20:31.270
You are

20:31.270 --> 20:32.880
the strongest blade to tear through

20:32.880 --> 20:34.280
the opponent's defense.

20:34.850 --> 20:37.840
There's another person
who has completely transformed.

20:37.840 --> 20:38.640
Lin Lu.

20:39.000 --> 20:40.160
The growth rate
of your total distance covered

20:40.160 --> 20:41.640
stands at 38%.

20:41.640 --> 20:43.370
You are at a whole new level now.

20:45.350 --> 20:46.590
Numbers don't lie.

20:47.000 --> 20:48.310
Every one of you

20:48.310 --> 20:49.560
has become stronger than before.

20:49.170 --> 20:51.660
[Distance covered by players]

20:50.510 --> 20:51.920
And more importantly,

20:52.270 --> 20:53.600
you are more united now.

21:01.830 --> 21:03.230
Although I never said it,

21:04.430 --> 21:05.830
whether you are sitting here

21:05.830 --> 21:07.030
loosely like this now

21:07.440 --> 21:08.440
or on the field,

21:09.160 --> 21:10.920
I can feel it very clearly

21:10.920 --> 21:12.590
that you are a whole.

21:14.680 --> 21:15.830
With these numbers,

21:17.070 --> 21:20.200
do you still think
you're bringing a knife to a gunfight?

21:23.640 --> 21:24.920
When I left the UK,

21:25.440 --> 21:26.840
I was actually very lost.

21:27.890 --> 21:30.750
I couldn't find the meaning
of football for a while.

21:31.440 --> 21:32.550
I felt at that time

21:33.270 --> 21:35.510
that the youth training there
was just a business,

21:35.510 --> 21:36.830
a cruel business.

21:38.310 --> 21:39.440
But I had no choice.

21:40.240 --> 21:42.310
This is the essence of competitive sports,

21:42.310 --> 21:43.160
cruelness.

21:45.240 --> 21:46.240
But now,

21:47.070 --> 21:48.240
I have found

21:49.440 --> 21:51.170
the meaning of football in you.

21:53.480 --> 21:55.880
Maybe you haven't realized it yourselves.

21:56.400 --> 21:57.960
On your path to victory,

21:57.960 --> 21:59.760
you've long stopped being soft.

22:01.030 --> 22:02.510
Long stopped.

22:03.030 --> 22:04.280
You yourselves

22:04.510 --> 22:06.240
are the meaning of football.

22:25.510 --> 22:26.370
Head-to-head,

22:27.440 --> 22:28.880
stone against stone.

22:30.200 --> 22:32.000
Find Yongchuan Hengjiu's flaw,

22:32.560 --> 22:34.360
and then score the winning goal.

22:41.510 --> 22:42.560
Wait,

22:42.860 --> 22:44.590
is no one going to say anything?

22:49.350 --> 22:51.640
Don't look at me.
I can't be the first to speak.

22:51.640 --> 22:53.750
If I do, my wise persona will be gone.

22:54.750 --> 22:55.640
Wise?

22:55.640 --> 22:57.770
Since when have you had a wise persona?

22:58.790 --> 23:00.190
I can't stand it anymore!

23:00.640 --> 23:01.750
Let's do this!

23:01.750 --> 23:03.680
Lin Lu, we can't be runners-up again!

23:03.680 --> 23:05.350
Right, we are the champions!

23:06.590 --> 23:07.680
Champions!

23:07.680 --> 23:09.920
-We are the champions!
-Champions!

23:09.920 --> 23:12.120
-We must be the champions!
-Champions!

23:12.440 --> 23:13.310
Let's go for training!

23:13.310 --> 23:13.880
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

23:13.880 --> 23:14.110
Let's go.

23:14.110 --> 23:16.920
-We must be the champions!
-7,300 meters.

23:17.220 --> 23:20.310
[Lin Lu] [Chen Jianghe]

23:17.350 --> 23:19.100
-Let's go.
-Guys.

23:19.310 --> 23:21.640
Watch me break through to 8 kilometers.

23:21.640 --> 23:22.350
Let's go.

23:22.350 --> 23:24.880
Let's practice the tactics
we learned today.

23:34.620 --> 23:36.640
You know what? This gym alone

23:36.640 --> 23:39.000
is bigger than all 5 gyms
I have at home combined.

23:39.000 --> 23:39.920
Also, also,

23:39.920 --> 23:41.400
the shower room inside

23:41.400 --> 23:42.920
is huge and smells good.

23:42.920 --> 23:44.680
Also, well...

23:44.680 --> 23:46.720
the... the heated pool.

23:48.640 --> 23:49.830
Thank you, Coach!

23:49.830 --> 23:52.200
Right, and the tactical meeting room
over there.

23:52.200 --> 23:53.640
It's all automated equipment,

23:53.640 --> 23:55.380
just like a spaceship in a movie!

23:55.380 --> 23:56.110
-Also...
-Yes.

23:56.110 --> 23:57.310
There's central AC,

23:57.310 --> 23:59.200
which far outperforms Ms. Lin's

23:59.200 --> 24:00.880
-old AC!
-Old AC.

24:01.720 --> 24:02.790
Right.

24:02.790 --> 24:03.510
Alright.

24:03.790 --> 24:05.030
Don't you want to play
to your heart's content?

24:05.030 --> 24:05.590
Go!

24:39.640 --> 24:40.640
No breakthrough.

24:40.960 --> 24:43.160
0.1 seconds away from 8 seconds. Again.

24:45.880 --> 24:47.610
Press forward, press forward.

25:00.510 --> 25:01.590
8.2 seconds.

25:02.200 --> 25:02.640
Again.

25:04.860 --> 25:06.320
Go for it! You've got this!

25:14.840 --> 25:15.810
8 seconds!

25:18.910 --> 25:23.530
[Three days before the finals]
[Yongchuan final field]

25:26.550 --> 25:27.550
Brothers,

25:27.550 --> 25:29.400
I never expected

25:29.400 --> 25:31.600
that we would still play the final here.

25:33.070 --> 25:34.240
It feels weird.

25:34.240 --> 25:35.590
What's weird?

25:36.510 --> 25:38.920
Get up where you fall.

25:39.310 --> 25:40.320
Brothers,

25:41.120 --> 25:43.430
let's enjoy this last match.

26:27.640 --> 26:28.400
Ms. Lin.

26:29.350 --> 26:30.160
Let's go.

26:30.160 --> 26:31.220
No training today.

26:33.270 --> 26:34.400
Go back and rest.

26:35.570 --> 26:36.670
The coach is right.

26:37.240 --> 26:39.480
Never be overly nervous before a match.

26:39.850 --> 26:42.310
Otherwise, you might crack under pressure.

26:42.790 --> 26:43.510
However,

26:43.920 --> 26:45.980
everyone must be back before 9:00 PM.

26:46.000 --> 26:46.840
-Got it.
-Got it.

26:46.840 --> 26:47.590
No problem!

26:47.590 --> 26:48.790
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

26:52.920 --> 26:54.260
Only 3 bottles left!

26:58.920 --> 27:00.430
The stylish kind.

27:00.590 --> 27:01.200
You've been ordering for so long.

27:01.200 --> 27:02.270
Are you done yet?

27:02.270 --> 27:03.790
Still picking. Still picking.

27:03.790 --> 27:05.000
Still ordering?

27:05.000 --> 27:07.480
-I'll change to this one.
-The earliest skin.

27:07.480 --> 27:08.830
This one is okay,

27:09.060 --> 27:11.220
but delivery takes 2 hours.

27:11.920 --> 27:13.110
Let's send a representative
to go buy some.

27:13.110 --> 27:14.240
-I won't go.
-The earliest one.

27:14.240 --> 27:15.000
Then who will go?

27:15.000 --> 27:16.750
And now it's updated to this.

27:16.750 --> 27:18.590
But this one is the coolest right now.

27:18.590 --> 27:19.880
And it has a car skin.

27:31.880 --> 27:33.960
-Stop hiding! It's you!
-Stop hiding! It's you!

27:33.960 --> 27:36.640
-Boss! It's you!
-It's you, Lu.

27:36.640 --> 27:39.270
-Boss! It's you!
-It's you, Lu!

27:40.310 --> 27:41.200
This is my bed.

27:41.920 --> 27:43.920
My bad, sorry.

27:44.830 --> 27:46.780
I'll make it for you.

27:46.900 --> 27:48.300
I want vanilla ice cream.

27:52.400 --> 27:54.350
Okay, okay.

27:54.350 --> 27:55.350
Then I'll just go buy my mom

27:55.350 --> 27:56.680
a birthday present.

27:57.030 --> 27:58.310
Let's go, Boss!

28:02.960 --> 28:04.720
I don't want to go!

28:06.200 --> 28:07.680
I don't want to go!

28:07.680 --> 28:08.440
Go.

28:08.440 --> 28:10.000
-Go. Go.
-Let's go.

28:10.750 --> 28:11.480
I want chocolate one!

28:11.480 --> 28:13.580
-I want blueberry one!
-Taro!

28:13.720 --> 28:15.850
-I want strawberry one!
-Vanilla one.

28:16.110 --> 28:16.680
I'll wait for you.

28:16.680 --> 28:17.680
-Okay.
-I'll wait for you.

28:17.680 --> 28:19.960
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

28:21.160 --> 28:22.160
I need to check quickly

28:22.160 --> 28:23.510
to see if we missed anything.

28:23.510 --> 28:24.590
We might need to buy more later.

28:24.590 --> 28:26.590
Boss, are you doing this on purpose?

28:26.990 --> 28:29.590
It's so heavy.
Won't you help me share the load?

28:29.640 --> 28:30.880
What's the rush?

28:30.880 --> 28:34.200
It's time to test the results
of your workout.

28:35.240 --> 28:37.480
I just remembered a saying.

28:37.480 --> 28:40.350
You are the company you keep.

28:41.350 --> 28:44.210
Boss, you've really been corrupted
by Wen Chengye.

28:44.350 --> 28:45.350
Let me tell you.

28:45.350 --> 28:47.110
Playing football is about winning.

28:47.110 --> 28:47.880
Right?

28:47.880 --> 28:49.640
Think about how Qin Qiechu

28:49.640 --> 28:51.350
looked at us back then.

28:51.830 --> 28:52.830
I just have to win.

28:52.830 --> 28:54.350
I won't let him show off to me.

28:54.350 --> 28:56.590
And that captain Fang Sulun,

28:57.200 --> 28:58.240
always pretending to be a good guy.

28:58.240 --> 28:59.900
Why is he copying my persona?

29:00.270 --> 29:01.750
He's really...

29:03.000 --> 29:04.370
Unbelievable.

29:04.440 --> 29:06.070
Speak of the devil.

29:07.430 --> 29:08.560
What a coincidence.

29:08.860 --> 29:10.910
[Yuan Yuan Vintage]
[Specialist Pre-Owned Luxury Boutique]

29:09.160 --> 29:11.420
Specialist Pre-Owned Luxury Boutique.

29:11.820 --> 29:12.670
What is it?

29:13.590 --> 29:16.270
I heard things are much cheaper
in this kind of shop.

29:16.270 --> 29:18.130
Let's go pick a good one for my mom.

29:19.240 --> 29:20.440
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

29:22.830 --> 29:24.000
Welcome.

29:24.000 --> 29:25.510
Feel free to look around.

29:25.640 --> 29:26.310
Hello.

29:38.920 --> 29:40.760
This ring is too expensive.

29:41.440 --> 29:41.920
Wait.

29:43.880 --> 29:46.160
Where did you get so much money?

29:46.510 --> 29:49.000
Boss, I saved my pocket money for a year,

29:49.000 --> 29:50.010
and it's all gone.

29:50.200 --> 29:51.960
So filial, Lu.

29:52.400 --> 29:53.880
You have no idea.

29:53.880 --> 29:55.680
I'm tanned like a piece of coal now.

29:55.680 --> 29:58.890
As soon as I get home,
my mom will definitely throw a huge fit.

29:58.890 --> 30:00.400
To shut her up,

30:00.400 --> 30:01.440
since her birthday is coming soon,

30:01.440 --> 30:03.100
I bought her a ring to coax her.

30:03.550 --> 30:05.830
You're getting as smart as I am.

30:05.830 --> 30:07.350
But honestly,

30:07.350 --> 30:08.510
this ring is really pretty.

30:08.510 --> 30:10.070
It really is pretty.

30:11.160 --> 30:12.310
But what I don't understand

30:12.310 --> 30:14.350
is how you spent so much time...

30:14.690 --> 30:17.540
[Basic Activity Organization]
[Alternative Forecasts]

30:17.700 --> 30:20.830
[Football Team
Training Record Progress Schedule]

30:24.890 --> 30:26.240
Three days left.

30:29.400 --> 30:30.440
Who is it?

30:33.830 --> 30:34.680
Coming.

30:35.640 --> 30:37.110
Li,

30:37.110 --> 30:38.440
why are you here?

30:38.440 --> 30:41.440
I'm here to cheer you and the kids on.

30:41.440 --> 30:42.680
I also brought you this,

30:42.680 --> 30:44.000
your favorite milk tea.

30:44.000 --> 30:45.350
Thanks.

30:45.350 --> 30:47.000
30% sugar, right?

30:50.030 --> 30:51.050
So,

30:51.090 --> 30:52.770
the competition is in 3 days.

30:52.880 --> 30:53.980
Are you nervous?

30:54.010 --> 30:55.380
Of course, I'm nervous.

30:55.440 --> 30:58.970
Much more nervous than I was sitting
my college entrance exams.

31:01.350 --> 31:03.270
It'll be fine.

31:03.640 --> 31:05.240
Our Wanxing will be fine.

31:05.350 --> 31:07.750
Just believe in yourself and be yourself.

31:15.350 --> 31:16.630
Your outfit

31:16.750 --> 31:19.080
looks way cooler than that in your videos.

31:19.400 --> 31:21.270
You watched our band's videos?

31:22.070 --> 31:23.470
How is it? Not bad, right?

31:24.490 --> 31:26.000
Right now, we have

31:26.000 --> 31:27.440
about 73 followers.

31:28.200 --> 31:29.590
73?

31:31.220 --> 31:34.290
There's still a little gap
before becoming internet famous.

31:34.290 --> 31:35.830
We just started the account.

31:35.830 --> 31:37.650
Having 73 is pretty good.

31:37.670 --> 31:40.030
And we also got our first commercial gig.

31:40.110 --> 31:41.880
Getting a commercial gig
with just 73 followers?

31:41.880 --> 31:43.110
That's impressive.

31:44.750 --> 31:47.190
It's just that the time of the first gig

31:47.220 --> 31:49.110
clashes with the match.

31:49.170 --> 31:50.590
So I probably won't be able to go

31:50.590 --> 31:52.850
and cheer for you guys in person that day.

31:57.200 --> 31:59.110
Did you come to me

31:59.110 --> 32:01.320
just because you feel guilty, didn't you?

32:01.320 --> 32:02.690
No way.

32:02.720 --> 32:03.790
I came...

32:05.030 --> 32:06.830
just because I wanted to see you.

32:07.590 --> 32:08.830
The other day,

32:09.360 --> 32:11.400
I made this myself, and...

32:11.720 --> 32:13.380
I just wanted to give it to you.

32:15.030 --> 32:16.350
You're too kind.

32:18.790 --> 32:19.570
Look.

32:19.790 --> 32:20.590
Do you like it?

32:21.750 --> 32:22.790
It's really pretty.

32:22.790 --> 32:23.550
Thank you.

32:25.790 --> 32:27.590
On my way here, I saw

32:27.590 --> 32:28.550
someone selling these.

32:28.550 --> 32:30.150
I thought they would suit me.

32:32.400 --> 32:34.270
Can you help me put them on?

32:34.750 --> 32:35.940
No problem.

32:36.520 --> 32:37.920
Let's go to the bathroom.

32:52.590 --> 32:53.270
All done.

32:56.750 --> 32:58.070
After those kids graduate,

32:58.070 --> 33:00.400
have you thought about
what you want to do?

33:02.920 --> 33:03.790
Not yet.

33:04.680 --> 33:06.410
I'll wait until they graduate.

33:06.750 --> 33:09.280
Right now, I just want to do my best

33:09.350 --> 33:12.070
to give them a result with no regrets.

33:14.640 --> 33:15.500
What about you?

33:20.510 --> 33:21.510
Me?

33:24.480 --> 33:26.030
Actually, I came back
to the country this time

33:26.030 --> 33:27.590
for a friend.

33:28.680 --> 33:30.590
She was in a tough spot back then

33:30.610 --> 33:31.870
and almost desperate.

33:34.830 --> 33:36.070
I thought,

33:37.350 --> 33:38.750
if I came back,

33:39.400 --> 33:41.310
I could be with her

33:41.730 --> 33:43.260
and help her out of the haze.

33:49.440 --> 33:52.160
But when I actually came back,
I found that

33:54.000 --> 33:56.110
she was much stronger than I thought.

33:58.030 --> 33:59.680
Whether I'm there or not,

34:01.610 --> 34:03.610
her smile is bright enough.

34:12.480 --> 34:13.480
Thank you,

34:14.110 --> 34:15.030
Li.

34:34.110 --> 34:35.440
Seal

34:35.920 --> 34:37.150
lifted.

35:04.360 --> 35:05.110
Lu,

35:05.920 --> 35:06.980
what are you doing?

35:07.320 --> 35:07.920
Drinking so much water.

35:07.920 --> 35:09.360
You wanna use the bathroom during training

35:09.360 --> 35:10.440
and slack off, right?

35:10.440 --> 35:11.320
I'm just thirsty.

35:11.320 --> 35:13.180
And I want to wet my whistle, okay?

35:13.360 --> 35:14.880
Just let him go.

35:15.510 --> 35:16.920
Every night,

35:16.920 --> 35:19.250
he yells about beating Yongchuan Hengjiu.

35:19.250 --> 35:20.540
Who else would be thirsty?

35:20.540 --> 35:21.980
Don't say that, Boss.

35:22.110 --> 35:25.030
If you hadn't forced me to watch the game
in the middle of the night,

35:25.030 --> 35:27.320
I wouldn't have dreamed about Hengjiu.

35:28.190 --> 35:29.720
You dreamed about the game?

35:29.760 --> 35:30.590
How was it?

35:31.190 --> 35:32.250
Did we win? Tell me.

35:33.280 --> 35:34.920
I didn't dream about the result,

35:34.920 --> 35:35.800
but

35:35.800 --> 35:38.150
I dreamed of Fang Sulun's big face.

35:40.670 --> 35:42.000
Then I was scared awake.

35:42.840 --> 35:43.800
Look at you.

35:44.280 --> 35:44.880
Let's go.

35:44.880 --> 35:45.920
To training.

35:50.550 --> 35:52.070
Hurry up.

35:52.070 --> 35:53.590
What's the rush?

35:54.150 --> 35:56.150
The last one there is a loser.

35:56.910 --> 36:04.880
[Hongjing No. 8 High's Dressing Room]

36:05.080 --> 36:08.370
[Yongchuan Provincial Youth Super League]

36:08.190 --> 36:09.630
Come on, hurry!

36:08.370 --> 36:11.740
[Hongjing No. 8 High School
versus Yongchuan Hengjiu]

36:10.000 --> 36:11.590
Come on, speed up!

36:13.550 --> 36:14.550
Come on, go for it.

36:18.230 --> 36:19.280
Qi Liang, mind your arms!

36:19.280 --> 36:20.180
Okay, okay.

36:20.710 --> 36:21.710
Come on, go for it.

36:21.960 --> 36:22.960
Come on, go for it.

36:28.440 --> 36:29.240
What's wrong?

36:30.480 --> 36:30.880
Come on.

36:30.880 --> 36:31.440
Did you sprain it?

36:31.440 --> 36:32.470
I'm fine.

36:32.470 --> 36:33.550
A little bit.

36:34.190 --> 36:35.550
It just hurts a little bit.

36:35.550 --> 36:36.360
Endure it.

36:36.360 --> 36:37.030
How is it?

36:39.250 --> 36:40.210
A little.

36:41.810 --> 36:42.740
Go back and rest.

36:42.750 --> 36:44.610
Ice it for 15 minutes at the hotel.

36:44.960 --> 36:45.890
I'm fine, Coach.

36:45.910 --> 36:46.760
I can still train.

36:46.760 --> 36:47.670
Go back and rest.

36:47.670 --> 36:49.520
Don't risk a big loss for a small gain.

36:49.520 --> 36:50.590
Who shares a room with him?

36:50.590 --> 36:51.200
Me.

36:52.190 --> 36:53.880
Coach, the match is tomorrow.

36:53.880 --> 36:55.610
Because the match is tomorrow,

36:55.840 --> 36:57.640
this training isn't important.

36:57.850 --> 36:58.730
Take him back.

36:58.760 --> 36:59.430
Come on.

37:00.610 --> 37:01.510
Let's go, Boss.

37:03.610 --> 37:04.670
Let me do it. Let me.

37:07.110 --> 37:08.960
-Be careful.
-Be careful.

37:09.320 --> 37:10.070
It's fine.

37:10.440 --> 37:11.440
Others continue.

37:16.550 --> 37:17.360
How long will this take?

37:17.360 --> 37:18.760
Let me carry you, come on.

37:20.070 --> 37:20.880
You carry me?

37:20.880 --> 37:22.190
Speed up! Speed up!

37:22.190 --> 37:23.920
The match is coming soon.

37:24.320 --> 37:26.440
If you get hurt,
I can't afford to compensate you.

37:26.440 --> 37:27.400
Be careful!

37:27.400 --> 37:28.530
Don't be like Qin Ao.

37:28.800 --> 37:29.910
Chen!

37:30.080 --> 37:31.550
-Come on.
-What's wrong?

37:31.550 --> 37:32.950
Boss sprained his ankle.

37:33.110 --> 37:35.060
You should help me
take him back to the hotel.

37:35.060 --> 37:36.180
Okay. Let's go.

37:37.320 --> 37:38.800
Are you okay?

37:38.800 --> 37:39.920
What could be wrong?

37:39.920 --> 37:40.880
Coach just won't let me practice.

37:40.880 --> 37:42.420
It's not a big deal today, but

37:42.420 --> 37:44.280
the main thing is the match tomorrow.

37:44.280 --> 37:45.880
You should be more careful.

37:45.880 --> 37:48.030
What could happen to a tough guy like me?

37:48.030 --> 37:49.760
Yeah, but you must be careful.

37:50.550 --> 37:51.440
Be careful.

37:51.440 --> 37:52.110
It's fine.

37:53.110 --> 37:54.070
Are you sure
you don't want to go to the hospital

37:54.070 --> 37:55.400
and get some medicine or something?

37:55.400 --> 37:56.550
It's just a minor injury.

37:56.550 --> 37:57.840
It'll heal faster that way.

37:57.840 --> 37:58.920
I'm a tough guy.

37:58.920 --> 37:59.920
Stop pretending.

37:59.920 --> 38:01.000
Go back and apply ice immediately.

38:01.000 --> 38:02.510
Then I'll get you
some anti-inflammatory medicine.

38:02.510 --> 38:03.920
-Okay.
-It's just that…

38:03.920 --> 38:05.320
the match is coming soon.

38:05.480 --> 38:07.070
Be a little more careful.

38:07.070 --> 38:09.070
Even injured, I can still beat them.

38:09.960 --> 38:10.760
Would it kill you not to pretend?

38:10.760 --> 38:12.730
Boss, do you have the room key?

38:13.070 --> 38:14.320
No, I gave it to you.

38:15.110 --> 38:17.340
-Look for it.
-I put it right here.

38:17.510 --> 38:18.370
I don't have it.

38:21.280 --> 38:23.610
Fang Sulun, what are you doing
in our room?

38:25.360 --> 38:25.920
Don't go!

38:25.920 --> 38:26.800
-I'll go!
-Catch him!

38:26.800 --> 38:28.030
-Okay, no problem!
-I'll go to the elevator,

38:28.030 --> 38:29.710
-Lu!
-I'll go with you!

38:30.400 --> 38:31.400
Stop right there!

38:37.000 --> 38:38.030
Stop right there!

38:40.070 --> 38:41.200
Stop right there!

38:44.320 --> 38:46.070
Brothers, hurry back.

38:46.070 --> 38:47.870
Our room got broken into. Hurry.

38:52.360 --> 38:53.880
Stop right there!

38:57.800 --> 38:59.600
Where do you think you’re going?

39:00.400 --> 39:01.200
Wait a minute!

39:06.710 --> 39:08.230
You can run, but you can't hide.

39:08.230 --> 39:10.160
Wait for us to catch you at Hengjiu?

39:13.360 --> 39:14.110
Confess, and you'll be treated leniently.

39:14.110 --> 39:15.440
Resist, and you'll be punished severely.

39:15.440 --> 39:18.040
Tell the truth,
what were you doing in our room?

39:20.360 --> 39:21.510
Why do we need an explanation?

39:21.510 --> 39:22.230
Ms. Lin,

39:22.230 --> 39:23.430
report him directly.

39:23.510 --> 39:25.550
Did Hengjiu send him
to check out our tactics?

39:25.550 --> 39:26.920
Yes, report him directly

39:26.920 --> 39:28.550
and disqualify him from the match.

39:28.550 --> 39:29.480
Did he really come

39:29.480 --> 39:30.550
to see our tactics?

39:30.550 --> 39:31.710
Are you stupid?

39:32.070 --> 39:34.400
They are Yongchuan Hengjiu.

39:34.630 --> 39:36.110
Why would they care about our tactics?

39:36.110 --> 39:37.190
Can you hurry

39:37.190 --> 39:38.520
and just say something?

39:38.550 --> 39:40.280
If you don't, I'll report you directly.

39:40.280 --> 39:41.470
-Don't!
-What are you doing?

39:41.470 --> 39:42.030
-What are you doing?
-What are you doing?

39:42.030 --> 39:43.150
Let go!

39:43.320 --> 39:44.320
-Let them handle it themselves.
-Let go!

39:44.320 --> 39:46.880
Let go!
Stop! What do you want?

39:56.920 --> 39:57.550
Lin Lu.

40:00.150 --> 40:02.550
Isn't this the ring
you bought for your mom?

40:03.130 --> 40:04.160
Call the police.

40:05.000 --> 40:07.110
I-I took the ring.

40:08.410 --> 40:09.740
But this is my own doing.

40:11.000 --> 40:12.800
I don't want it to affect my team.

40:17.550 --> 40:18.750
This is my mom's ring.

40:19.400 --> 40:21.150
Lin Lu bought the ring for his mom.

40:21.150 --> 40:22.800
How did it become your mom's?

40:25.650 --> 40:26.960
This ring

40:27.320 --> 40:28.840
was a birthday present

40:29.920 --> 40:31.650
my dad bought my mom when I was 8.

40:32.550 --> 40:33.920
Then why was it in the store?

40:33.920 --> 40:35.190
Did it fly there?

40:39.400 --> 40:40.930
Because my mom passed away.

40:44.570 --> 40:46.130
What are you talking about?

40:46.470 --> 40:47.590
Make it clear.

40:52.890 --> 40:54.500
Three months after my mom died,

40:54.500 --> 40:55.790
my dad remarried.

40:56.510 --> 40:58.240
The stepmother didn't like me.

40:58.260 --> 40:59.220
She thought

40:59.340 --> 41:01.400
I was a third wheel in their marriage.

41:02.000 --> 41:03.190
So my dad

41:03.190 --> 41:05.190
sent me to Hengjiu boarding school.

41:06.440 --> 41:07.540
I carried this ring

41:07.560 --> 41:09.120
with me every day.

41:10.230 --> 41:11.800
But when I went to boarding school,
I was afraid of losing it,

41:11.800 --> 41:13.800
so I locked it in the cabinet at home.

41:15.030 --> 41:16.820
But she must have found it.

41:17.630 --> 41:20.060
She thought it was bad luck
because it was my mom's

41:20.060 --> 41:20.940
and sold it.

41:25.230 --> 41:25.840
Later, my dad and I

41:25.840 --> 41:27.280
had a fight over it.

41:27.480 --> 41:29.510
I pieced together the torn receipt

41:29.510 --> 41:31.710
to find the pre-owned luxury boutique.

41:32.320 --> 41:33.360
But I didn't expect

41:33.360 --> 41:34.150
the price...

41:34.760 --> 41:36.000
So you got anxious.

41:36.000 --> 41:37.320
I've been working to earn money

41:37.320 --> 41:38.880
to buy it back.

41:38.910 --> 41:40.250
But I didn't expect

41:40.280 --> 41:41.970
that you two bought it yesterday.

41:41.970 --> 41:43.970
When I saw you bought it,

41:44.000 --> 41:44.920
I don't know what happened to me.

41:44.920 --> 41:46.030
I just went crazy.

41:46.030 --> 41:47.070
I only knew this ring

41:47.070 --> 41:48.590
had to stay with me.

41:54.760 --> 41:56.030
But I was desperate.

41:56.060 --> 41:58.000
I was wrong about this.

41:59.230 --> 41:59.900
Lin Lu,

42:00.280 --> 42:02.030
I will return the money
for the ring to you.

42:02.030 --> 42:03.840
I will give you all my savings.

42:03.840 --> 42:06.100
If it's not enough, I'll write you an IOU.

42:10.180 --> 42:11.220
I'm sorry, Lin Lu.

42:12.510 --> 42:13.230
This is the only thing

42:13.230 --> 42:14.920
my mom left me.

42:29.440 --> 42:30.360
I'm sorry.

42:30.720 --> 42:32.520
I can accept any punishment.

42:33.190 --> 42:34.250
I can also drop out.

42:35.210 --> 42:36.960
But I don't want my own business

42:37.800 --> 42:38.860
to affect Hengjiu.

42:45.510 --> 42:47.310
Do you have anything else to ask?

42:51.510 --> 42:53.230
You guys decide this matter yourselves.
